Where to Watch

A German mail-order bride encounters prejudice when she comes to Minnesota to marry a Norwegian immigrant farmer just after World War I. Elizabeth Reaser and Tim Guinee star in this poignant and lyrical romantic drama. Alan Cumming, John Heard, Alex Kingston, Ned Beatty. Directed by Ali Selim.
